HTML
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Soft Touch</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f5f5f5; /* Light background for content */
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif; /* Basic font stack */
        }

        .about-us {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px; /* Add some padding for content */
        }

            .about-us h1,
            .about-us h2 {
                margin-bottom: 20px; /* Add space between headings */
            }

            .about-us p {
                line-height: 1.5; /* Increase line spacing for readability */
            }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="about-us">
       
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>
            Welcome to Soft Touch, your destination for luxurious, high-quality skincare. At Soft Touch, we believe that everyone deserves to feel pampered and confident in their skin. Our mission is to create lotions that not only nourish and hydrate but also bring a touch of indulgence to your daily routine.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>
            Soft Touch was founded with a simple yet profound goal: to transform the everyday skincare routine into a moment of self-care and relaxation. Inspired by nature's most beneficial ingredients, our products are carefully crafted to provide the ultimate in skin hydration and nourishment.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
            We are committed to using only the finest natural and sustainably sourced ingredients. Each lotion is formulated with a blend of essential oils, vitamins, and plant extracts designed to moisturize, protect, and rejuvenate your skin. We believe in transparency, and every product we offer is cruelty-free, paraben-free, and free from harmful chemicals.
        </p>

        <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Natural Ingredients: We prioritize the use of organic and eco-friendly ingredients to ensure our products are gentle on your skin and kind to the planet.</li>
            <li>Innovative Formulas: Our team of experts combines the latest skincare science with traditional remedies to create lotions that deliver real, noticeable results.</li>
            <li>Commitment to Quality: Every batch of lotion undergoes rigorous testing to ensure it meets our high standards of quality and safety.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our Promise</h2>
        <p>
            At Soft Touch, customer satisfaction is our top priority. We are dedicated to providing you with exceptional products and outstanding service. Whether you have dry, sensitive, or normal skin, our range of lotions is designed to meet your unique needs and enhance your natural beauty.
        </p>

        <h2>Join Our Community</h2>
        <p>
            We invite you to join the Soft Touch community and experience the difference our products can make. Follow us on social media, subscribe to our newsletter for exclusive offers and skincare tips, and share your Soft Touch journey with us.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you for choosing Soft Touch. Your skin deserves the best, and we're here to deliver it.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>